Notes / Best Practices
	•	Never throw from ErrorWriter — it’s a last‑resort safety net.
	•	Keep error blobs small (capped at 256 KB here). Adjust MAX_BYTES as you wish.
	•	All error blobs start with tag status=New; if you later add a replay job, you can flip to Resolved or Dead.
	•	Use lifecycle rules on the errors container (e.g., delete after 30 days).

